--- control: a MergeTree table advertises the optimization, so length(arr) is rewritten to arr.size0 ---
control-rewritten
--- ENGINE = URL('file://...') delegates to File, which disables the optimization: length(arr) is NOT rewritten ---
subcolumn-not-rewritten
--- PREWHERE on a plain column is allowed (delegate's supportedPrewhereColumns contains it) ---
1
--- PREWHERE on a default-expression column is rejected (delegate's supportedPrewhereColumns excludes it) ---
prewhere-default-col-rejected
